&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 3&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

questions.statement:
&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The following question has&amp;nbsp;two premises and two conclusions. If the premises re assumed to be true (irrespective of factuality), then, in respect of each of the items given below, which of the following conclusions follow logically?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Premises: All metals are grey in colour. Some metals are heavy.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Conclusion:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;I. All heavy metals are grey in colour.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;II. All light metals are not grey in colour.&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/08/F1_Madhuri_UPSC_19.08.2022_D1.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 209px; height: 102px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Conclusion:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;I. All heavy metals are grey in colour. &amp;rarr; True (As, All metals are grey in colour. Some metals are heavy &amp;rarr; So the metals that are heavy all are grey in colour)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/08/F1_Madhuri_UPSC_19.08.2022_D2.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 263px; height: 120px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;II. All light metals are not grey in colour. &amp;rarr; False (No reference related to light metal is given in the statement)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &amp;lsquo;Only I&amp;rsquo; follows.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/confusion-points-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Confusion Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Please understand that it is not given that All that metals are heavy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
The meaning of the given statement is that &amp;#39;all those metals which are heavy are grey.&lt;/p&gt;

