&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;II. Some parrots are butterflies - False (No definite relation given between &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;butterflies&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;parrots&lt;/span&gt;, so it can be possible only).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, Neither conclusion I or II follow.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 3&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

