&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Conclusion II: No cat is pupil &amp;rarr; False (This is definitely false)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;But,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Conclusions I and II form a complementary pair.&lt;/p&gt;
Hence, &amp;ldquo;either conclusion I or conclusion II&amp;rdquo; follows.

